should not wear mourning clothes.

00:07:10.750 --> 00:07:12.160
Today I am not a princess.

00:07:13.680 --> 00:07:15.280
You don't need to protect me.

00:07:16.340 --> 00:07:18.020
If Father knows, I will bear

00:07:19.630 --> 00:07:20.890
the punishment alone.

00:07:22.360 --> 00:07:24.090
I apologize for my disrespect.

00:07:24.360 --> 00:07:27.600
Wanyu Yuedan,
Palace Chief of Biluo Palace, has arrived.

00:07:29.240 --> 00:07:32.970
Cheng Yunpao, Vice Island Master
of Camellia Island, has arrived.

00:07:34.870 --> 00:07:38.200
Puzhu, Pavilion Master
of Tianjing Pavilion, has arrived.

00:07:56.110 --> 00:07:57.360
Master Puzhu,

00:07:57.360 --> 00:08:00.220
