as the head of the Sword Alliance,

00:08:51.200 --> 00:08:52.000
not come?

00:08:52.580 --> 00:08:54.550
No matter how important
Tang Lici's business is,

00:08:54.550 --> 00:08:55.410
he should come.

00:08:55.750 --> 00:08:57.870
This is Master Shao's funeral, after all.

00:08:57.870 --> 00:08:59.200
