00:09:19.360 --> 00:09:20.120
Everyone,

00:09:20.390 --> 00:09:21.960
we are gathered here today

00:09:22.180 --> 00:09:24.430
to mourn the leader of the Sword Alliance.

00:09:24.430 --> 00:09:26.280
Master Shao was attacked by Ghostly Peony

00:09:26.280 --> 00:09:27.800
on his way out

00:09:28.690 --> 00:09:30.220
and unfortunately passed away.

00:09:30.220 --> 00:09:31.720
It is a great loss
to the martial arts world

00:09:31.720 --> 00:09:33.050
and a sorrow to jianghu.

00:09:33.890 --> 00:09:36.020
We should carry on Master Shao's will,

00:09:36.400 --> 00:09:37.800
eliminate Fengliu Shop,

00:09:37.800 --> 00:09:39.060
and kill Ghostly Peony

00:09:39.350 --> 00:09:41.630
to avenge Master Shao.

